    "competitive_position": "TF Bank occupies a distinctive niche in the European banking landscape. Unlike full-service digital banks (Revolut, N26) or pure payment companies (Klarna), TF Bank combines consumer lending, credit cards, and e-commerce payments on a single proprietary platform across 14 countries. Key competitors include Bank Norwegian (Nordax), Advanzia Bank, and Klarna in different segments. TF Bank's competitive advantages are: (1) proprietary tech platform enabling rapid multi-country scaling, (2) disciplined credit risk management delivering consistent profitability, (3) diversified revenue across three segments, and (4) lean operating model. The bank is smaller than major universal banks but grows faster and with higher ROE.",
